reviewText: Two attractive women in this dvd, Luscious Latasha, a cute short african american lady does ok in one match against amy prime time lee, considering her size. The other attractive lady is Athena , a beautiful african american lady ,  her full title is Athena the wrestling goddess, and she is definitely beautiful like a goddess. Athena  has a match with this chick with a beer belly who looks like she just ate a large pancake breakfast  before the match and to top it off the stupid announcer says  out loud he is the aforementioned chick with a beer belly's side.  Other than that great dvd.

The WSU is a small venued but serious promotion(serious = no T&A). The matches I found most entertaining were ODB vs Portia Perez, Angel Orsini vs Alicia, Amber vs Brittney Force, Jana & Cindy Rogers vs The Belle Saints. No matches sucked but no matches were awesome either.
